{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850433263,"sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","part":{"id":"prt_d78ef261d001DwJ2vrBrCOv9lY","messageID":"msg_d78ef1ee4001nN0dPnEAXmNoJn","sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_92312b722c694a1eac872ad0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n2: \n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: **Language:** Python\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `pack` 子命令，作为 AI Agent 生命周期管理的入口点。`pack` 命令负责验证工作区结构、加载或创建元数据、合并 CLI 覆盖选项、处理语言特定依赖、生成 Dockerfile，并将工作区打包为可供后续 `build`、`publish`、`invoke` 操作使用的就绪状态。\n10: \n11: 当前 Python CLI 已定义 `pack` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `PackRuntime` 类结构，但需要完整的实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为。\n12: \n13: ## 范围\n14: \n15: ### 包含\n16: \n17: 1. **`pack` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n18:    - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `agent_name`, `language`, `entrypoint`, `port`, `build_mode`, `description`, `output`, `verbose`\n19:    - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示 `agent_name`、`workspace_path`、`metadata_path`\n20:    - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"pack\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1\n21:    - Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n22: \n23: 2. **`PackRuntime` 类完整实现** (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`)\n24:    - `pack(workspace_path, **options)` — 主入口，编排完整流程\n25:    - `_validate_workspace_structure(workspace_path)` — 验证路径存在且为目录\n26:    - `_load_or_create_metadata(workspace_path, options)` — 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`（回退 `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`）或创建新元数据\n27:    - `_apply_option_overrides(metadata, options)` — 合并 CLI 选项到 `AgentMetadata`\n28:    - `_validate_language_compatibility(workspace_path, metadata)` — 分发到语言特定验证\n29:    - `_validate_python_compatibility(workspace_path)` — 检查至少一个 `*.py` 文件\n30:    - `_validate_java_compatibility(workspace_path)` — 检查 `pom.xml` 存在\n31:    - `_process_dependencies(workspace_path, metadata)` — 分发到语言特定依赖处理\n32:    - `_process_python_dependencies(workspace_path)` — 验证 `requirements.txt`\n33:    - `_process_java_dependencies(workspace_path)` — 验证 Maven/Gradle 设置\n34:    - `_generate_dockerfile(workspace_path, metadata)` — 生成语言对应的 Dockerfile（如不存在）\n35:    - `_generate_python_dockerfile(metadata)` — Python Dockerfile 模板\n36:    - `_generate_java_dockerfile(metadata)` — Java Dockerfile 模板\n37:    - `_update_pack_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, dockerfile_path)` — 持久化最终元数据\n38:    - `_prepare_output_path(workspace_path, output_path)` — 解析输出目录\n39:    - `_infer_entrypoint(workspace_path, language)` — 从工作区文件自动推断入口点\n40: \n41: 3. **`MetadataService` 实现** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n42:    - `load_metadata(workspace_path)` — YAML 加载带回退链\n43:    - `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` — 写入 `agent_metadata.yaml`，使用 `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)` 和 `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\n44:    - `update_metadata(workspace_path, updates)` — 加载、合并、保存\n45:    - `validate_workspace(workspace_path)` — 语言特定验证\n46:    - `_validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` — Python 工作区验证\n47:    - `_validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` — Java 工作区验证\n48: \n49: 4. **`AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n50:    - 所有字段定义及验证器：`validate_language` → `['python', 'java']`；`validate_build_mode` → `['local', 'cloud']`；`validate_port` → `1..65535`\n51: \n52: 5. **`MetadataOptions` 数据类** (`agentcube/models/pack_models.py`)\n53:    - 所有可选字段及默认值\n54:    - `from_options(cls, options)` 类方法\n55: \n56: ### 不包含\n57: \n58: - `build`、`publish`、`invoke`、`status` 命令的实现（由其他 AR 覆盖）\n59: - `DockerService` 的完整实现（仅 `pack` 需要 Dockerfile 生成，不需要 Docker SDK 交互）\n60: - `KubernetesProvider` / `AgentCubeProvider` 实现\n61: - Python CLI 到 Go CLI 的迁移\n62: - CI/CD pipeline 变更\n63: \n64: ## 架构概要\n65: \n66: ### 组件关系\n67: \n68: ```\n69: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n70: │                    CLI Layer (Typer)                     │\n71: │  agentcube/cli/main.py: pack() command                   │\n72: │  - 解析选项 → 调用 PackRuntime.pack()                    │\n73: │  - Rich 输出 / _handle_error()                           │\n74: └──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n75:                        │\n76: ┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐\n77: │                   Runtime Layer                          │\n78: │  agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py: PackRuntime          │\n79: │  - 编排验证 → 元数据 → 依赖 → Dockerfile 流程            │\n80: │  - 依赖 MetadataService 加载/保存元数据                  │\n81: └──────────┬─────────────────────────────┬────────────────┘\n82:            │                             │\n83: ┌──────────▼──────────┐    ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐\n84: │  Metadata Layer     │    │  Models Layer               │\n85: │  MetadataService    │    │  AgentMetadata (Pydantic)   │\n86: │  - YAML I/O         │    │  MetadataOptions (dataclass)│\n87: │  - 验证             │    │  - 字段验证器               │\n88: └─────────────────────┘    └─────────────────────────────┘\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### 目录结构\n92: \n93: ```\n94: cmd/cli/\n95: ├── pyproject.toml                 # 项目元数据、依赖、console script\n96: ├── agentcube/\n97: │   ├── __init__.py                # __version__, 导出 app, runtimes\n98: │   ├── cli/\n99: │   │   ├── __init__.py            # CLI 子包标记\n100: │   │   └── main.py                # Typer app, pack 命令, _handle_error\n101: │   ├── models/\n102: │   │   └── pack_models.py         # MetadataOptions dataclass\n103: │   ├── runtime/\n104: │   │   ├── __init__.py            # 重新导出 runtimes + MetadataOptions\n105: │   │   └── pack_runtime.py        # PackRuntime 类\n106: │   ├── services/\n107: │   │   ├── __init__.py            # Services 包 docstring\n108: │   │   └── metadata_service.py    # AgentMetadata, MetadataService\n109: │   └── operations/\n110: │       └── __init__.py            # 占位模块 docstring\n111: └── examples/\n112:     ├── hello-agent/\n113:     │   └── main.py                # Python 示例 agent\n114:     └── math-agent/\n115:         └── main.py                # Python 示例 agent\n116: ```\n117: \n118: ## 影响分析\n119: \n120: ### 直接影响\n121: \n122: | 文件 | 变更类型 | 说明 |\n123: |------|----------|------|\n124: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | 修改 | 实现 `pack()` 命令体，调用 `PackRuntime` |\n125: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | 实现 | 完整实现所有私有方法 |\n126: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 实现 | `AgentMetadata` + `MetadataService` |\n127: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | 实现 | `MetadataOptions` 数据类 |\n128: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | 确认 | 确保 `PackRuntime` 导出正确 |\n129: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | 确认 | 确保 re-exports 正确 |\n130: \n131: ### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n132: \n133: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0` — CLI 框架（已有依赖）\n134: - `pydantic>=2.0.0` — 元数据验证（已有依赖）\n135: - `pyyaml>=6.0` — YAML 序列化（已有依赖）\n136: - `rich>=13.0.0` — Progress spinner、格式化输出（已有依赖）\n137: - `packaging>=23.0` — 版本解析（已有依赖）\n138: \n139: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n140: \n141: - **AR: `build` 命令** — 依赖 `pack` 生成的 Dockerfile 和元数据\n142: - **AR: `publish` 命令** — 依赖 `pack` 和 `build` 的输出\n143: - **AR: `invoke` 命令** — 依赖 `publish` 部署后的 endpoint\n144: \n145: ### 无影响的组件\n146: \n147: - `BuildRuntime`、`PublishRuntime`、`InvokeRuntime`、`StatusRuntime` — 本 AR 不修改\n148: - `DockerService` — 本 AR 仅生成 Dockerfile 文本，不调用 Docker SDK\n149: - `KubernetesProvider` / `AgentCubeProvider` — 不涉及\n150: - Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n151: \n152: ### 风险评估\n153: \n154: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n155: |------|------|----------|\n156: | 工作区验证过于严格导致用户摩擦 | 中 | 初始实现最小必要检查，根据反馈迭代 |\n157: | Dockerfile 生成与现有文件冲突 | 低 | 如 Dockerfile 已存在则跳过生成；后续可添加 `--force` |\n158: | 元数据 schema 演进导致向后不兼容 | 中 | 使用 Pydantic `Optional` 字段和合理默认值；YAML 加载兼容旧格式 |\n159: | Python/Java 依赖处理遗漏边界情况 | 中 | 针对示例工作区编写集成测试覆盖 |\n160: \n161: ## 备选方案\n162: \n163: ### 1. 单一 PackRuntime 类编排所有步骤（✅ 选定方案）\n164: \n165: **做法**：`PackRuntime` 类包含所有私有方法，在 `pack()` 中顺序调用。\n166: \n167: **优点**：\n168: - 逻辑集中，易于理解和调试\n169: - 与 spec 中定义的类结构一致\n170: - 测试时可按方法隔离 mock\n171: \n172: **缺点**：\n173: - 类可能变大（~15 个方法）\n174: - 语言特定逻辑混在同一类中\n175: \n176: **决策**：采用。与现有 spec 定义一致，且 Size M 的范围内可控。\n177: \n178: ### 2. 策略模式分离语言处理\n179: \n180: **做法**：定义 `LanguageHandler` 接口，`PythonHandler` 和 `JavaHandler` 实现，`PackRuntime` 委托给 handler。\n181: \n182: **优点**：\n183: - 语言扩展更清晰（添加新语言只需新 handler）\n184: - 单一职责更严格\n185: \n186: **缺点**：\n187: - 增加抽象层，对当前仅 2 种语言来说过度设计\n188: - 与 spec 中定义的类结构不一致\n189: \n190: **决策**：不采用。当前仅支持 Python/Java，策略模式增加复杂度。可在未来添加第 3 种语言时重构。\n191: \n192: ## 实现要点\n193: \n194: ### `pack` 命令流程\n195: \n196: ```python\n197: @app.command()\n198: def pack(...):\n199:     workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()\n200:     try:\n201:         with Progress() as progress:\n202:             task = progress.add_task(\"Packaging...\", total=None)\n203:             runtime = PackRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n204:             result = runtime.pack(workspace_path, **options)\n205:         # Rich 输出: agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path\n206:     except Exception as e:\n207:         _handle_error(e, \"pack\", verbose)\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### `PackRuntime.pack()` 内部流程\n211: \n212: ```python\n213: def pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n214:     self._validate_workspace_structure(workspace_path)\n215:     metadata = self._load_or_create_metadata(workspace_path, options)\n216:     metadata = self._apply_option_overrides(metadata, options)\n217:     self._validate_language_compatibility(workspace_path, metadata)\n218:     self._process_dependencies(workspace_path, metadata)\n219:     dockerfile_path = self._generate_dockerfile(workspace_path, metadata)\n220:     self._update_pack_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, dockerfile_path)\n221:     output_path = self._prepare_output_path(workspace_path, options.get(\"output\"))\n222:     return {\n223:         \"agent_name\": metadata.agent_name,\n224:         \"workspace_path\": str(workspace_path),\n225:         \"metadata_path\": str(workspace_path / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"),\n226:         \"dockerfile_path\": str(dockerfile_path) if dockerfile_path else None,\n227:         \"output_path\": str(output_path),\n228:     }\n229: ```\n230: \n231: ### 元数据加载回退链\n232: \n233: ```\n234: 1. agent_metadata.yaml (首选)\n235: 2. agent.yaml (回退)\n236: 3. metadata.yaml (回退)\n237: 4. 创建新的 AgentMetadata (如果都不存在)\n238: ```\n239: \n240: ### Dockerfile 生成策略\n241: \n242: - 如工作区已有 `Dockerfile`，跳过生成\n243: - Python: 基于 `python:3.10-slim`，复制 `requirements.txt` → `pip install` → 复制代码 → 设置 entrypoint\n244: - Java: 基于 `maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-17` 构建，`eclipse-temurin-17-jre` 运行，复制 `pom.xml` → `mvn package` → 复制 jar → 设置 entrypoint\n245: \n246: ### 入口点推断逻辑\n247: \n248: - Python: 查找 `main.py` → 第一个 `.py` 文件 → `python main.py`\n249: - Java: 查找 `pom.xml` 中的 `mainClass` → 默认 `java -jar target/*.jar`\n250: \n251: ## 验收标准\n252: \n253: - [ ] `pack` 命令接受所有指定选项，使用正确默认值\n254: - [ ] `workspace` 默认 `.`，可通过 `-f` / `--workspace` 覆盖\n255: - [ ] 工作区验证捕获缺失目录、非目录路径\n256: - [ ] Python 工作区无 `.py` 文件时抛出 `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n257: - [ ] Java 工作区无 `pom.xml` 时抛出相应错误\n258: - [ ] 元数据加载通过 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml` 回退\n259: - [ ] CLI 选项正确合并到现有元数据（不覆盖未指定的字段）\n260: - [ ] 为 Python 和 Java agent 生成正确的 Dockerfile\n261: - [ ] 成功消息显示 `agent_name`、`workspace_path`、`metadata_path`\n262: - [ ] 错误处理打印红色消息 + traceback（verbose），退出码 1\n263: - [ ] Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n264: - [ ] `--verbose` 启用 `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`\n265: - [ ] `AgentMetadata` 验证器拒绝不支持的 `language` / `build_mode` 和无效 `port` 范围\n266: - [ ] 元数据保存使用 `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)` 和 `exclude_none=True`\n267: \n268: ## 状态\n269: \n270: - [ ] 提案审查\n271: - [ ] 实现\n272: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 272 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** M\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `pack` 子命令，作为 AI Agent 生命周期管理的入口点。`pack` 命令负责验证工作区结构、加载或创建元数据、合并 CLI 覆盖选项、处理语言特定依赖、生成 Dockerfile，并将工作区打包为可供后续 `build`、`publish`、`invoke` 操作使用的就绪状态。\n\n当前 Python CLI 已定义 `pack` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `PackRuntime` 类结构，但需要完整的实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **`pack` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `agent_name`, `language`, `entrypoint`, `port`, `build_mode`, `description`, `output`, `verbose`\n   - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示 `agent_name`、`workspace_path`、`metadata_path`\n   - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"pack\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775850433253,"end":1775850433260}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850434485,"sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","part":{"id":"prt_d78ef2b75001D5bFs1R4zGA3I0","messageID":"msg_d78ef1ee4001nN0dPnEAXmNoJn","sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4100be8f32d743a184704b23","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\n2: \n3: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\n4: \n5: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\n6: \n7: | Path | Role |\n8: |------|------|\n9: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\n10: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\n11: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\n12: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\n13: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n14: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\n15: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\n16: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\n17: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\n18: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\n19: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\n20: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\n21: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |\n22: | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | `DockerService` |\n23: | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | `KubernetesProvider` |\n24: | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | `AgentCubeProvider` |\n25: | `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` | Placeholder module docstring (no symbols) |\n26: | `examples/hello-agent/main.py` | Example agent |\n27: | `examples/math-agent/main.py` | Example agent |\n28: \n29: **Setuptools packages** (from `pyproject.toml` `[tool.setuptools]`):  \n30: `agentcube`, `agentcube.cli`, `agentcube.runtime`, `agentcube.operations`, `agentcube.services`  \n31: *(Note: `agentcube.models` is not listed in `[tool.setuptools] packages` but is imported; packaging may rely on setuptools discovery for subpackages — reconstruct imports from source as above.)*\n32: \n33: ## Console script entry point\n34: \n35: ```toml\n36: [project.scripts]\n37: kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"\n38: ```\n39: \n40: Typer app object: `app = typer.Typer(name=\"agentcube\", help=\"...\", no_args_is_help=True, rich_markup_mode=\"rich\", add_completion=False)`.\n41: \n42: ## Typer — root callback\n43: \n44: ```python\n45: def main(\n46:     version: Optional[bool] = typer.Option(\n47:         None, \"--version\", help=\"Show version and exit\",\n48:         callback=version_callback, is_eager=True,\n49:     ),\n50:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", \"-v\", help=\"Enable verbose output\"),\n51: ) -> None:\n52:     \"\"\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management.\"\"\"\n53: ```\n54: \n55: ## Typer — `pack`\n56: \n57: ```python\n58: def pack(\n59:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n60:     agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", help=\"Override the agent name\"),\n61:     language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", help=\"Programming language (python, java)\"),\n62:     entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", help=\"Override the entrypoint command\"),\n63:     port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--port\", help=\"Port to expose in the Dockerfile\"),\n64:     build_mode: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--build-mode\", help=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\"),\n65:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", help=\"Agent description\"),\n66:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for packaged workspace\"),\n67:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n68: ) -> None:\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ## Typer — `build`\n72: \n73: ```python\n74: def build(\n75:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n76:     proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\", help=\"Custom proxy URL for dependency resolution\"),\n77:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\"),\n78:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for build artifacts\"),\n79:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n80: ) -> None:\n81: ```\n82: \n83: ## Typer — `publish`\n84: \n85: ```python\n86: def publish(\n87:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n88:     version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--version\", help=\"Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)\"),\n89:     image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-url\", help=\"Image repository URL (required in local build mode)\"),\n90:     image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-username\", help=\"Username for image repository\"),\n91:     image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-password\", help=\"Password for image repository\"),\n92:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", help=\"Agent description\"),\n93:     region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--region\", help=\"Deployment region\"),\n94:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\"),\n95:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"),\n96:     node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--node-port\", help=\"Specific NodePort to use (30000-32767) for K8s deployment\"),\n97:     replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--replicas\", help=\"Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1)\"),\n98:     namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--namespace\", help=\"The namespace for the deployment\"),\n99:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n100: ) -> None:\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ## Typer — `invoke`\n104: \n105: ```python\n106: def invoke(\n107:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n108:     payload: str = typer.Option(\"{}\", \"--payload\", help=\"JSON-formatted input passed to the agent\"),\n109:     header_list: Optional[List[str]] = typer.Option(None, \"--header\", help=\"Custom HTTP headers (e.g., 'Authorization: Bearer token'). Can be specified multiple times.\"),\n110:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"),\n111:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n112: ) -> None:\n113: ```\n114: \n115: ## Typer — `status`\n116: \n117: ```python\n118: def status(\n119:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n120:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"),\n121:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n122: ) -> None:\n123: ```\n124: \n125: ## Helper functions (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n126: \n127: ```python\n128: def version_callback(value: bool) -> None: ...\n129: def _handle_error(e: Exception, command_name: str, verbose: bool) -> None: ...  # prints, typer.Exit(1)\n130: ```\n131: \n132: ## Runtime classes\n133: \n134: ### `PackRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`)\n135: \n136: ```python\n137: class PackRuntime:\n138:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n139:     def pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n140:     def _validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n141:     def _load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n142:     def _apply_option_overrides(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n143:     def _validate_language_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n144:     def _validate_python_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n145:     def _validate_java_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n146:     def _process_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n147:     def _process_python_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n148:     def _process_java_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n149:     def _generate_dockerfile(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Optional[Path]: ...\n150:     def _generate_python_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str: ...\n151:     def _generate_java_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str: ...\n152:     def _update_pack_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata, dockerfile_path: Optional[Path]) -> None: ...\n153:     def _prepare_output_path(self, workspace_path: Path, output_path: Optional[str]) -> Path: ...\n154:     def _infer_entrypoint(self, workspace_path: Path, language: str) -> str: ...\n155: ```\n156: \n157: ### `BuildRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\n158: \n159: ```python\n160: class BuildRuntime:\n161:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n162:     def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n163:     def _increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata) -> Any: ...\n164:     def _validate_build_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None: ...\n165:     def _build_local(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n166:     def _build_cloud(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n167:     def _update_build_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, build_result: Dict[str, str], tag: str = \"latest\") -> None: ...\n168: ```\n169: \n170: ### `PublishRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n171: \n172: ```python\n173: class PublishRuntime:\n174:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n175:     def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n176:     def _publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n177:     def _publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n178:     def _prepare_image_for_publishing(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n179:     def _prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n180:     def _prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n181:     def _update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None: ...\n182: ```\n183: \n184: ### `InvokeRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`)\n185: \n186: ```python\n187: class InvokeRuntime:\n188:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n189:     def invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Any: ...\n190:     def _validate_invoke_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> Tuple[Any, str, str]: ...\n191:     async def _invoke_agent_via_agentcube(self, agent_id: str, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]], endpoint: str, workspace_path: Path) -> Any: ...\n192:     async def _direct_http_invocation(self, endpoint: str, payload: Dict[str, Any], headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]], workspace_path: Path) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n193: ```\n194: \n195: **Implementation note:** `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube` only assigns `response` inside `if endpoint.startswith(\"http\"):`; if the condition is false, `return response` may raise `UnboundLocalError` (as of extracted source).\n196: \n197: ### `StatusRuntime` (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n198: \n199: ```python\n200: class StatusRuntime:\n201:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n202:     def get_status(self, workspace_path: Path, provider: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n203:     def _get_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n204:     def _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n205: ```\n206: \n207: ## `DockerService` (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n208: \n209: ```python\n210: class DockerService:\n211:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n212:     def check_docker_available(self) -> bool: ...\n213:     def build_image(\n214:         self,\n215:         dockerfile_path: Path,\n216:         context_path: Path,\n217:         image_name: str,\n218:         tag: str = \"latest\",\n219:         build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n220:     ) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n221:     def get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n222:     def _get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n223:     def _format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str: ...\n224:     def push_image(\n225:         self,\n226:         image_name: str,\n227:         registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n228:         username: Optional[str] = None,\n229:         password: Optional[str] = None,\n230:     ) -> Dict[str, str]: ...\n231:     def _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None: ...\n232:     def _tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> None: ...\n233:     def remove_image(self, image_name: str) -> bool: ...\n234: ```\n235: \n236: ## `MetadataService` (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n237: \n238: ```python\n239: class MetadataService:\n240:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n241:     def load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n242:     def save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n243:     def update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n244:     def validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool: ...\n245:     def _validate_python_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n246:     def _validate_java_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n247: ```\n248: \n249: ## `KubernetesProvider` (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\n250: \n251: ```python\n252: class KubernetesProvider:\n253:     def __init__(\n254:         self,\n255:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n256:         verbose: bool = False,\n257:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n258:     ) -> None: ...\n259:     def _ensure_namespace(self) -> None: ...\n260:     def deploy_agent(\n261:         self,\n262:         agent_name: str,\n263:         image_url: str,\n264:         port: int,\n265:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n266:         replicas: int = 1,\n267:         node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n268:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n269:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n270:     def _create_deployment(\n271:         self,\n272:         name: str,\n273:         image_url: str,\n274:         port: int,\n275:         entrypoint: Optional[str],\n276:         replicas: int,\n277:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]],\n278:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n279:     def _create_service(self, name: str, port: int, node_port: Optional[int]) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n280:     def wait_for_deployment_ready(self, name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None: ...\n281:     def get_agent_status(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n282:     def delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n283:     def _sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str: ...\n284: ```\n285: \n286: ## `AgentCubeProvider` (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\n287: \n288: ```python\n289: class AgentCubeProvider:\n290:     def __init__(\n291:         self,\n292:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n293:         verbose: bool = False,\n294:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n295:     ) -> None: ...\n296:     def _ensure_namespace(self) -> None: ...\n297:     def deploy_agent_runtime(\n298:         self,\n299:         agent_name: str,\n300:         image_url: str,\n301:         port: int,\n302:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n303:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n304:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n305:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n306:         readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n307:         readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n308:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n309:     def _sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str: ...\n310:     def get_agent_runtime(self, name: str, namespace: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]: ...\n311: ```\n312: \n313: CR API: `group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`, `version=\"v1alpha1\"`, `plural=\"agentruntimes\"`.\n314: \n315: ## `AgentMetadata` (Pydantic `BaseModel`)\n316: \n317: | Field | Type | Default | `Field(..., description=...)` |\n318: |-------|------|---------|--------------------------------|\n319: | `agent_name` | `str` | (required) | Unique name identifying the agent |\n320: | `description` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Human-readable summary |\n321: | `language` | `str` | `\"python\"` | Programming language used |\n322: | `entrypoint` | `str` | (required) | Command to launch the agent |\n323: | `port` | `int` | `8080` | Port exposed by the agent runtime |\n324: | `build_mode` | `str` | `\"local\"` | Build strategy: local or cloud |\n325: | `region` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Deployment region |\n326: | `version` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Semantic version string for publishing |\n327: | `image` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Container image information |\n328: | `auth` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Authentication configuration |\n329: | `requirements_file` | `Optional[str]` | `\"requirements.txt\"` | Python dependency file |\n330: | `registry_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry URL for image publishing |\n331: | `registry_username` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry username |\n332: | `registry_password` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry password |\n333: | `agent_endpoint` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent endpoint URL |\n334: | `workload_manager_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | URL for the Workload Manager |\n335: | `router_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | URL for the Router |\n336: | `readiness_probe_path` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Path for the readiness probe |\n337: | `readiness_probe_port` | `Optional[int]` | `None` | Port for the readiness probe |\n338: | `agent_id` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent ID assigned by AgentCube |\n339: | `session_id` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | The session ID for the agent |\n340: | `k8s_deployment` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Kubernetes deployment information |\n341: \n342: Validators: `validate_language` → `['python','java']` lowercase; `validate_build_mode` → `['local','cloud']` lowercase; `validate_port` → `1..65535`.\n343: \n344: ## `MetadataOptions` (`agentcube/models/pack_models.py`)\n345: \n346: Dataclass fields (all `Optional` unless noted):\n347: \n348: | Field | Type | Default |\n349: |-------|------|---------|\n350: | `agent_name` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n351: | `language` | `Optional[str]` | `'python'` |\n352: | `entrypoint` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n353: | `port` | `Optional[int]` | `8080` |\n354: | `build_mode` | `Optional[str]` | `'local'` |\n355: | `requirements_file` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n356: | `description` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n357: | `workload_manager_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n358: | `router_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n359: | `readiness_probe_path` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n360: | `readiness_probe_port` | `Optional[int]` | `8080` |\n361: | `registry_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n362: | `registry_username` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n363: | `registry_password` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n364: | `agent_endpoint` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n365: \n366: ```python\n367: @classmethod\n368: def from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\": ...\n369: ```\n370: \n371: ## Dependencies (`cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`)\n372: \n373: **`[project]` dependencies:**\n374: \n375: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0`\n376: - `pydantic>=2.0.0`\n377: - `pyyaml>=6.0`\n378: - `httpx>=0.24.0`\n379: - `docker>=6.0.0`\n380: - `rich>=13.0.0`\n381: - `packaging>=23.0`\n382: - `importlib-resources>=6.0.0`\n383: - `semver>=3.0.0`\n384: \n385: **Optional `[project.optional-dependencies]`:**\n386: \n387: - `k8s`: `kubernetes>=28.0.0`\n388: - `dev`: `pytest>=7.4.0`, `pytest-asyncio>=0.21.0`, `pytest-cov>=4.1.0`, `ruff>=0.1.0`, `mypy>=1.5.0`, `pre-commit>=3.3.0`, `kubernetes>=28.0.0`\n389: - `test`: `pytest>=7.4.0`, `pytest-asyncio>=0.21.0`, `pytest-cov>=4.1.0`, `pytest-mock>=3.11.0`, `httpx-mock>=0.10.0`\n390: \n391: **Python:** `requires-python = \">=3.10\"`.\n392: \n393: ## Top-level exports (`agentcube/__init__.py`)\n394: \n395: - `__version__ = \"0.1.0\"`\n396: - `__author__ = \"AgentCube Community\"`\n397: - `__email__ = \"agentcube@volcano.sh\"`\n398: - Imports: `app`, `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`, `InvokeRuntime`\n399: - `__all__` = `[\"app\", \"PackRuntime\", \"BuildRuntime\", \"PublishRuntime\", \"InvokeRuntime\"]`  \n400:   (`StatusRuntime` is not exported here.)\n\n(End of file - total 400 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\n\nSource root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\n\n## Package layout (every module path and role)\n\n| Path | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\n| `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n| `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md","time":{"start":1775850434476,"end":1775850434483}}}}
