{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850669420,"sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","part":{"id":"prt_d78efc48d001Bl1r3Z5isUn33q","messageID":"msg_d78ef5ffd00131ZPGDlAxbJCd9","sessionID":"ses_287142419ffeQOq2kV3FLICynY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_2992e6c54405495c8b292b90","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-020/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-020/design.md`, `changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## T1. 创建 Python CLI 项目脚手架\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/` 目录\n- [ ] 1.2 创建 `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`，包含：\n  - `name = \"agentcube\"`, `requires-python = \">=3.10\"`, `version = \"0.1.0\"`\n  - `[project] dependencies`: typer[all]>=0.9.0, pydantic>=2.0.0, pyyaml>=6.0, httpx>=0.24.0, docker>=6.0.0, rich>=13.0.0, packaging>=23.0, importlib-resources>=6.0.0, semver>=3.0.0\n  - `[project.optional-dependencies]`: k8s, dev, test（与 cli-toolkit/design.md 依赖表一致）\n  - `[project.scripts]`: `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n  - `[tool.setuptools] packages`: agentcube, agentcube.cli, agentcube.runtime, agentcube.operations, agentcube.services\n  - `[tool.pytest.ini_options]`: testpaths = [\"tests\"]\n  - `[tool.ruff]`, `[tool.mypy]` 基础配置\n- [ ] 1.3 创建包目录结构：\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py`（`__version__ = \"0.1.0\"`, `__author__`, `__email__`, 导出占位）\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n  - `cmd/cli/agentcube/operations/__init__.py`\n  - `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py`\n- [ ] 1.4 创建 `.gitignore`（`__pycache__/`, `*.pyc`, `.pytest_cache/`, `dist/`, `build/`, `*.egg-info/`）\n- [ ] 1.5 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n- [ ] 1.6 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 和 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认工具链可用\n\n**Verification:** `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` exit 0；`python -c \"import agentcube; print(agentcube.__version__)\"` 输出 `0.1.0`；ruff 和 mypy 无致命错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 MetadataOptions 数据类 — agentcube/models/pack_models.py\n\n- [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n- [ ] 2.2 定义 `MetadataOptions` dataclass，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §MetadataOptions 表一致：\n  `agent_name: Optional[str] = None`\n  `language: Optional[str] = \"python\"`\n  `entrypoint: Optional[str] = None`\n  `port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n  `build_mode: Optional[str] = \"local\"`\n  `requirements_file: Optional[str] = None`\n  `description: Optional[str] = None`\n  `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n  `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n- [ ] 2.3 实现 `@classmethod from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\"` 类方法：\n  - 从 options dict 中提取已知字段，忽略未知字段\n  - 返回 `MetadataOptions` 实例\n- [ ] 2.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py`\n- [ ] 2.5 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_Defaults`：无参构造 → 所有字段为默认值\n- [ ] 2.6 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Full`：完整 options dict → 字段完全匹配\n- [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Partial`：部分 options dict → 缺失字段为默认值\n- [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_UnknownFields`：含未知字段 → 忽略未知字段，已知字段正确\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T3. 实现 AgentMetadata Pydantic 模型 — agentcube/services/metadata_service.py（部分）\n\n- [ ] 3.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- [ ] 3.2 定义 `AgentMetadata(BaseModel)`，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §AgentMetadata 表一致：\n  `agent_name: str`（required）\n  `description: Optional[str] = None`\n  `language: str = \"python\"`\n  `entrypoint: str`（required）\n  `port: int = 8080`\n  `build_mode: str = \"local\"`\n  `region: Optional[str] = None`\n  `version: Optional[str] = None`\n  `image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n  `auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n  `requirements_file: Optional[str] = \"requirements.txt\"`\n  `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n  `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = None`\n  `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None`\n  `router_url: Optional[str] = None`\n  `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None`\n  `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None`\n  `agent_id: Optional[str] = None`\n  `session_id: Optional[str] = None`\n  `k8s_deployment: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n- [ ] 3.3 实现 Pydantic v2 validators（`@field_validator`）：\n  - `validate_language`: 限制为 `['python', 'java']`，转小写\n  - `validate_build_mode`: 限制为 `['local', 'cloud']`，转小写\n  - `validate_port`: 范围 1–65535\n- [ ] 3.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py`\n- [ ] 3.5 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidCreation`：合法字段 → 模型创建成功\n- [ ] 3.6 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Python`：`language=\"Python\"` → 规范化为 `\"python\"`\n- [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Java`：`language=\"java\"` → 通过\n- [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Rejected`：`language=\"nodejs\"` → `ValidationError`\n- [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Local`：`build_mode=\"local\"` → 通过\n- [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Cloud`：`build_mode=\"cloud\"` → 通过\n- [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Rejected`：`build_mode=\"hybrid\"` → `ValidationError`\n- [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Valid`：`port=8080` → 通过\n- [ ] 3.13 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Zero`：`port=0` → `ValidationError`\n- [ ] 3.14 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Overflow`：`port=70000` → `ValidationError`\n- [ ] 3.15 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ModelDump`：`model_dump(exclude_none=True)` 不包含 None 字段\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Port validation 和 §Build mode validation 和 §Language validation 全部场景\n\n---\n\n## T4. 实现 MetadataService — YAML 加载/保存与回退链\n\n- [ ] 4.1 在 `metadata_service.py` 中定义 `MetadataService` 类：\n  - `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n- [ ] 4.2 实现 `load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata`：\n  - 按回退链尝试加载：`agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`\n  - 使用 `yaml.safe_load()` 解析 YAML\n  - 将 dict 传入 `AgentMetadata(**data)` 构造模型\n  - 三个文件都不存在时返回 `None`\n- [ ] 4.3 实现 `save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n  - 使用 `yaml.dump(metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True), default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)`\n  - 写入 `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n- [ ] 4.4 实现 `update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n  - 先调用 `load_metadata` 加载现有元数据\n  - 如不存在则创建默认 `AgentMetadata`\n  - 合并 updates dict 到现有模型（使用 `model_copy(update=updates)` 或等价方式）\n  - 调用 `save_metadata` 保存\n  - 返回更新后的 `AgentMetadata`\n- [ ] 4.5 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py`\n- [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_PrimaryExists`：`agent_metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n- [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_FirstFallback`：仅 `agent.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n- [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_SecondFallback`：仅 `metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n- [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_NoneExist`：三个文件都不存在 → 返回 `None`\n- [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_RoundTrip`：保存后重新加载 → 数据一致\n- [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_ExcludeNone`：保存的 YAML 不包含 null 值\n- [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_Format`：YAML 使用 `default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False`\n- [ ] 4.13 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_Merge`：部分更新 → 未更新字段保留原值\n- [ ] 4.14 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_CreateNew`：无现有文件 → 创建新元数据\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Metadata loading with fallback chain 全部 4 个场景\n\n---\n\n## T5. 实现工作区验证 — PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure\n\n- [ ] 5.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n- [ ] 5.2 定义 `PackRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)`\n- [ ] 5.3 实现 `_validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n  - 路径不存在 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path does not exist: {workspace_path}\")`\n  - 路径不是目录 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path is not a directory: {workspace_path}\")`\n- [ ] 5.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py`\n- [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_ValidDirectory`：有效目录 → 无异常\n- [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_NotExists`：路径不存在 → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_IsFile`：路径是文件而非目录 → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_SymlinkToDirectory`：符号链接指向目录 → 通过\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Workspace validation — not a directory 场景\n\n---\n\n## T6. 实现元数据加载与创建 — PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata\n\n- [ ] 6.1 实现 `_load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n  - 调用 `self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)` 尝试加载\n  - 如返回 None，从 options 构造 `MetadataOptions`，再用默认值创建新 `AgentMetadata`\n  - 新元数据的 `agent_name` 从 workspace 目录名推断（如 options 中未提供）\n- [ ] 6.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_metadata_load.py`\n- [ ] 6.3 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_ExistingFile`：存在 `agent_metadata.yaml` → 加载并返回\n- [ ] 6.4 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_FallbackChain`：仅 `agent.yaml` 存在 → 通过回退链加载\n- [ ] 6.5 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_FromOptions`：无文件，有 options → 从 options 创建\n- [ ] 6.6 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_InferName`：无文件无 agent_name → 从目录名推断\n- [ ] 6.7 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_Defaults`：无文件无 options → 使用全部默认值\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_metadata_load.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T7. 实现选项合并 — PackRuntime._apply_option_overrides\n\n- [ ] 7.1 实现